HEADWORD: Runcinate
<hw>Run"ci*nate</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[L.
<ets>runcinatus</ets>, p. p. of <ets>runcinare</ets> to plane off, fr.
<ets>runcina</ets> a plane.]</ety> <fld>(Bot.)</fld> <def>Pinnately cut
